description: This is something I kinda threw together. This is a brief rendition of the MLP Theme song.  "Zecora" was the working title because the theme just seemed to fit her character. I used a soundfont that is not supported by this site so I had to upload it to youtube first. You can hear the song in the videoscore (the sheet music is muted).
title: My Little Pony: Tribal Rendition (videoscore)
